STATE of New Jersey, Petitioner-Respondent,
v.
NEW JERSEY LAW ENFORCEMENT SUPERVISORS ASSOCIATION, Respondent-Petitioner. 079666
C-107 Sept. Term 2017 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 28, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004723-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
